      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Please read through the whole guide: <a href=\"http://developer.android.com/tools/publishing/app-signing.html#signapp\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">developer.android.com/tools/publishing/app-signing.html#sign&zwnj;&#8203;app</a>  Alternatively, you can simply sign your app using Eclipse."
