    "creation_date" : 1443117041,
    "answer_id" : 32767818,
    "question_id" : 21457538,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For -tsa option enter the next one:</p>\n\n<pre><code>jarsigner -verbose **-tsa http://timestamp.comodoca.com/rfc3161** -sigalg SHA1withRSA -digestalg SHA1 -keystore your_keystor_name.keystore YourAPK.apk youralias_key\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
